ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: It was a great class to learn about colloids. I would definitely recommend it as a very informative class.
It is highly recommended, I feel this class is very useful. It addition to colloidal science, it covers thermodynamics, physics and some math.
Recommended for people who do colloidal or electrochemistry.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This was a great introductory course to colloid science, and it will help me in my future research.
